xt-ndpi (5.1.0+git20260623) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial DKMS packaging of the nDPI xt_ndpi netfilter kernel module
    (xt-ndpi-dkms), built from the vel21ripn/nDPI fork (kernel 6.8.x fixes).
    DKMS builds xt_ndpi against the running kernel and auto-rebuilds it on
    every kernel upgrade.
  * Add xt-ndpi-iptables: the userspace libxt_ndpi.so xtables extension that
    provides the iptables "-m ndpi" match, built from the same revision.
  * Add xt-ndpi-filter: a configurable systemd rule engine (/usr/sbin/ndpi-filter)
    that applies nDPI iptables rules from /etc/default/ndpi-filter to a chain
    (default DOCKER-USER), re-applying on Docker restart.

